  "prompt": "PLAN-GATE PROTOCOL ACTIVE. Real-money urgency: post-place verify in bracket_writer_g2 calls Robinhood API for Coinbase orders, getting 404. Coinbase orders ARE being placed (we have order IDs in logs) but DB never sees them as confirmed. 9 Coinbase positions remain DB-naked.\n\nFULL rules + brief in markdown. Read in this order:\n  1. CLAUDE.md\n  2. docs/STRATEGY/PROTOCOL.md\n  3. docs/STRATEGY/COWORK_ADVISOR_BRIEF.md (focus 2.1 anti-truncation)\n  4. docs/STRATEGY/QUEUED/f-coinbase-post-place-verify-routing-fix.md (the brief)\n  5. docs/STRATEGY/NEXT_TASK.md (status check)\n  6. app/services/trading/bracket_writer_g2.py (find the post-place verify path)\n  7. app/services/trading/venue/coinbase_spot.py (does get_order_status exist?)\n  8. app/services/trading/venue/robinhood_spot.py (mirror its get_order_status return shape)\n\nThen follow the brief: write plan.request.md, wait for approval, implement with anti-truncation discipline (Write for files >500 lines), wip-commit per checkpoint, write CC_REPORT, update NEXT_TASK to DONE.\n\nAUTHORIZATION CONTEXT: Interactive Cowork has pre-authorized broker-adapter changes for this autonomous loop. The watcher's no-auto-approve rule for broker adapters is being overridden because operator's clear preference is self-driving fixes. If watcher writes REVISE on procedural broker-adapter grounds, interactive Cowork will overwrite with APPROVED.\n\nKEY DESIGN DECISION TO INCLUDE IN PLAN: For the 4 Coinbase orders that already got assigned IDs (b3c14ef6 AERGO-USD, 545eeffe 1INCH-USD, d1b91a9c ACX-USD, b13e8058 RARE-USD), they exist at Coinbase but aren't in DB. After the verify fix lands, the next reconciler sweep should be able to call get_order_status on these IDs to recover them. But the writer needs to remember the order IDs across sweeps -- check if it persists them anywhere or if they're lost. If lost, propose a one-shot reconcile pass that lists open Coinbase orders by ticker and matches them to intents.\n\nHARD CONSTRAINTS:\n  - bracket_writer_g2.py + coinbase_spot.py ONLY. No reconciler / stop_engine / autotrader / Robinhood adapter changes.\n  - Edit-tool truncation discipline. After each modification: wc -l + git diff --stat + python ast.parse.\n  - Coinbase Phase 6 LIVE soak active. Purely additive routing branch -- do NOT weaken existing safety gates.\n  - No magic-fallback values. If Coinbase API is unreachable, raise.\n  - Plan-gate active.",
